{"tid":528431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"81歲阿伯連續十年　每天往鄰居家丟排泄物","createTime":"2018-01-13T18:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T03:08:00.000Z","uid":56533,"like":115,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"908d127c486c7db1f98e4dd7ea58b42acc2eaac9","tid":528431,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180112/640_d7e98762a534ef95f0bc4164945e4cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180112%2F640_d7e98762a534ef95f0bc4164945e4cd4.jpg&h=206ab2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本名古屋市1名81歲阿伯，連續10年以上每天都會往鄰居家丟大小便、垃圾，鄰居受不了後找警察前往警戒，在阿伯丟棄時以違反廢棄物處理法現行犯逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《東海TV》報導，遭到逮捕的名古屋市81歲阿伯今泉英，於10日晚上10點左右，往鄰居家扔排泄物，遭到警方逮捕。報導指出，受害鄰居去年4月曾向警方投訴，本月10日晚間，警員到現場進行調查，看到今泉英將裝滿排泄物的容器，往受害鄰居家中丟後將其逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n鄰居控訴，「門的手把被排泄物沾到，都腐壞掉了」，且門口旁邊的牆都有汙垢殘留，連對講機也沒辦法使用，「一年365天都會來丟，不知道他為何會這樣做」。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，今泉英至少丟了10年以上的大小便，對於警方的調查，今泉英則是反駁，「我沒有丟棄任何廢棄物，為何要逮捕我」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180112/1277553/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1277553%2F&d=JmjKm%2FXIeRW2n9jwsKbyyi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4bfb4a91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1277553%2F&h=25f8ee1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180112/1277553/</a>"},{"pid":"05576b40c2eb317b8739c01aa695b04911def73c","tid":528431,"uid":7954,"like":356,"dislike":3,"score":353,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce0bf711bda165234c1ad54b29315075138341ba","tid":528431,"uid":1654,"like":198,"dislike":1,"score":197,"quote":{"pid":"05576b40c2eb317b8739c01aa695b04911def73c","tid":528431,"uid":7954,"like":356,"dislike":3,"score":35